create a django project
inside the created project, create an app
in the project settings file, install the app
inside the app folder create a urls file
i the project urls, import include
create a default url/path and include your apps urls file

in the app urls file, within the urls pattern, create a default path/urls and
specify the function. dont forget to import views.

in the views files, define the functions reffernced in the app urls

